{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SaaS Product - Innovate & Elevate</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #3498db;\n            --secondary-color: #abcdef;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #2c3e50;\n            --footer-text-color: #ecf0f1;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 3rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 6rem 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n   