ckground);\n            color: var(--footer-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--footer-text-color);\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>InnovateFlow</h1>\n        <p>Streamline Your Workflow, Amplify Your Results.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Unlock Your Team's Potential</h2>\n            <p>InnovateFlow is the all-in-one platform designed to boost productivity and drive collaboration for modern businesses.</p>\n            <a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Key Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Seamless Collaboration</h3>\n                    <p>Work together in real-time with intuitive tools and shared workspaces.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Advanced Analytics</h3>\n                    <p>Gain insights into your performance with comprehensive dashboards and reports.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Task Management</h3>\n                    <p>Organize, track, and manage all your projects with ease.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Customizable Workflows</h3>\n                    <p>Adapt InnovateFlow to fit your unique business processes.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"testimonials\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"InnovateFlow has revolutionized how our team operates. Productivity has soared!\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Jane Doe, CEO of TechSolutions</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"The ease of use and powerful features make it indispensable for our daily operations.\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- John Smith, Project Manager</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"pricing\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Flexible Pricing Plans</h2>\n            <p>Choose the plan that best suits your needs.</p>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Basic</h3>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$19<span>/month</span></p>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li>10 Users</li>\n                        <li>Core Features</li>\n                        <li>Basic Support</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Choose Plan</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Pro</h3>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$49<span>/month</span></p>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li>50 Users</li>\n                        <li>All Core Features</li>\n                        <li>Advanced Analytics</li>\n                        <li>Priority Support</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Choose Plan</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Enterprise</h3>\n                    <p class=\"price\">Custom</p>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li>Unlimited Users</li>\n                        <li>All Features</li>\n                        <li>Dedicated Account Manager</li>\n                        <li>24/7 Support</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 InnovateFlow. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}